title: Happily Ever After
description: The Neo Pearl collection from OWN YOUR STORY is the audacious but wearable outside-the-box take on pearls that your customers have been waiting for! Own Your Story is a third generation family-owned brand with a passion for gorgeous, well-priced, fashionable jewelry.

title: Lab Grown and Lovely
description: A gorgeous pioneer in the world of lab-grown diamond fashion jewelry, LARK & BERRY offers precious metal designs set with their cultured diamonds. The new Halo Sapphire collection, with warm rose gold and pretty pink sapphires, is rosy perfection.

title: After the Ring
description: The stunning new After the Ring collection from ROYAL CHAIN is bridal, but not in the way that you’re thinking: it’s dedicated to everything but the rings. Think bridal shower jewels, wedding party sets, mother of the bride bling, and more — with retail starting at just $29.

title: Impossibly Chic
description: FACET BARCELONA’s newly extended trends collection offers a wide range of dynamic, ultra-chic yellow gold and diamond designs. With sensuous curving lines and a glamorous but minimalist aesthetic that fashionable shoppers are sure to love, these elegant styles demand a second and third look.

title: Ring D
description: Ring D is a home security and smart home company owned by Amazon. Ring manufactures home security products that incorporate outdoor surveillance cameras, including the Ring Video smart doorbell, and hosts an app, Neighbors, for online social sharing of captured footage among users.
